title: Grateful Dead Live at Atlanta Municipal Auditorium on 1971-11-11
lineage: --Burned direct to CD from Cassette using a ~1989 TC-WE475 Stereo Cassette Deck  to a ~2001 Sony CD Burner. Converted raw wav files to 14Hkbps / 44khz using Roxio import Cd function of Roxio Music Creator suite (2009). Pitch Corrected somewhat using Adobe Audtion CC 2018. Tracking, editing and patching using Roxio Sound Editor (2009).
